        {
            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "@clason @justinmk thanks for the reasonably balanced responses, a bit more extensive than in this case. I tried to formulate the previous post to respect the reviewers' choices (and indirectly their time, including in case it makes sense to close this one), while also expressing my confusion and trying to understand their motivations. I've been passively reviewing Nvim project changes for years, and even if I learn relatively little from them, I'm gaining some insight, especially regarding which solutions are close to trivial (like this one).\r\n\r\nI wasn't sure about the title of this PR since the problem became two-part.\r\n\r\nI already asked @luukvbaal for help here (before I wrote any correct test) and didn't want to be pushy in drawing his attention again.\r\n\r\nThe puc-lua tests failing with empty error messages make me suspect they're false positives. In either case, I have no idea what to do with them on my end.\r\n\r\nIn general, thanks also for the time spent on the changes in the meantime, which pushed this one into oblivion. I could remember about the rebase myself.",
