        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Yes the idea of this prompt with ext_messages (even after previous decoupling of press-enter prompts) was that `wait_return()` is called in places where the user absolutely needs to read a message. Going over all callsites had been on my to do list as that obviously isn't the case yet.\r\n\r\nThis looks like a good incremental PR meanwhile. Thanks @przepompownia and sorry for the delay. Pushed a small typo fix for for the PUC Lua failure.",
